narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Again, the arts library policy is extremely difficult to work with (one book/day)... This has to change. Waiting for a machine to scan every page I need to write a paper is such a waste of time and energy that could be saved by simply checking out more books.
